  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project will provide counselling to  7200 children  who are severely affected by disasters or have been exposed to violence in the past years.  2) It will build the capacity of 360 educators, counselors, caregivers,   from 360 classrooms   who work with the children who have experienced trauma through their day-to-day experiences in their families and communities. 3) A playground for Child will be established   for the Tree of Life Practice, sports and playing, stories  and games.</narrative>
